<Layout title="Teman Telkomsel (Web2SMS) - Mas Muhammad" description="An enterprise SMS broadcast platform for Telkomsel enabling member management, community grouping, and scheduled SMS broadcasting with bulk MSISDN import. Built with CodeIgniter PHP framework on Oracle database using Modular HMVC architecture. The primary subscriber engagement system serving millions of Telkomsel customers.">
